<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Christie Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Christie Park is administer by the Strathcona Christie Aspen Community Association, along with Strathcona Park and Aspen Wood, and operates public tennis courts, an outdoor hockey and skating rink and a sports/playing field. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The joint community centre for the three communities has a gym, commercial kitchen, lounge, meeting rooms, a sound system and an indoor fireplace, as well as a deck with a great view and a loft. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community association hosts a variety of programs, including sports, fitness, dance, senior programs and childcare. Westside Recreation Centre has a fitness centre and swimming pool open to the public.</p>
        </div>
